column2: SELECT TOP # A.ID_#,A.Name,A.RAdeg,A.DEdeg,A.logMBH,D.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_tight_flag,D.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_medium_flag,D.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_tight_debiased,D.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_medium_debiased,D.t0#_smooth_or_features_a0#_smooth_debiased,D.t0#_smooth_or_features_a0#_features_or_disk_debiased FROM   MyDB.Liu2# as A   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( A.RAdeg, A.DEdeg, #/#.) AS B   INNER JOIN SpecPhotoAll as C on B.objID=C.objID   INNER JOIN zoo2MainSpecz as D on C.specobjID=D.specobjID WHERE   D.t0#_spiral_a0#_spiral_debiased>=# INTO Liu2#_zoo2MainSpeczSpiral
